      "description": "Stretching between the Indonesian islands of Lombok and Bali, the Lombok Strait has risen in economic importance in recent years. Far deeper than the Strait of Malacca, the passage has become an increasingly popular alternate route for the largest container ships. The Indonesian government has worked to encourage this shift by expanding local infrastructure. As it has grown in significance, however, the Lombok Strait has seen increased threats from piracy and environmental degradation.",
